  "description": "A long, dark-hulled ship is sailing on a slightly choppy, deep blue body of water. The ship has a prominent red and white section towards the rear and a tall white cabin with a yellow stripe at the bow. It is equipped with a large crane for loading and unloading cargo. In the background, a cityscape rises with various buildings, including taller skyscrapers and lower industrial structures, all shrouded in a light haze. The sky is a clear, bright blue with a few wispy clouds. A concrete pier extends into the water.",
